{111}{}{我好久没在赌场看到食尸鬼了。。。但是-等等。哈！我把你当成食尸鬼。。。嗯，但别以为我会道歉。 -- I haven't seen ghouls in this casino for a long time... But - wait a minute. Ha! I took you for a ghoul... Hmm, but don't think I'll apologize.}
