{133}{}{为什么这很重要？ -- And why does that matter?}
#{134}{}{That seems like an obvious lie, although, since we are partners and share common interests, I'll close my eyes to it. But bear in mind, that the mutual respect of Mr. Thompson and his team is more important for me than your services.}
{134}{}{这似乎是一个明显的谎言，不过，既然我们是合作伙伴，有着共同的利益，我就闭眼不谈了。但请记住，汤普森先生和他的团队的相互尊重对我来说比你们的服务更重要。 -- That seems like an obvious lie, although, since we are partners and share common interests, I'll close my eyes to it. But bear in mind, that the mutual respect of Mr. Thompson and his team is more important for me than your services.}
#{135}{}{That's a fair statement. I have no objections, but bear in mind that the mutual respect of Mr. Thompson and his team is more important than your services.}
{135}{}{这是一个公平的说法。我不反对，但请记住，汤普森先生和他的团队的相互尊重比你们的服务更重要。 -- That's a fair statement. I have no objections, but bear in mind that the mutual respect of Mr. Thompson and his team is more important than your services.}
#{136}{}{If you are looking for conflicts, do it elsewhere. I respect Mr. Thompson and intend to continue our... Mutual business with him. We will not turn a blind eye if you continue to cross our paths.}
{136}{}{如果你在寻找冲突，那就到别处去做。我尊敬汤普森先生并打算继续我们的。。。和他做生意。如果你继续横穿我们的道路，我们不会视而不见。 -- If you are looking for conflicts, do it elsewhere. I respect Mr. Thompson and intend to continue our... Mutual business with him. We will not turn a blind eye if you continue to cross our paths.}
