#{151}{}{Communications? With whom... ?}
{151}{}{通讯？和谁一起？ -- Communications? With whom... ?}
#{152}{}{Jordan Bishop recommended me to work for you.}
{152}{}{乔丹・毕肖普推荐我为你工作。 -- Jordan Bishop recommended me to work for you.}
#{153}{}{But your administrator advised me to speak with you.}
{153}{}{但你的管理员建议我和你谈谈。 -- But your administrator advised me to speak with you.}
#{154}{}{Listen, I wasn't born yesterday. I've handled a lot of jobs in my time...}
{154}{}{听着，我不是昨天出生的。我这段时间做了很多工作。。。 -- Listen, I wasn't born yesterday. I've handled a lot of jobs in my time...}
#{155}{}{What about this package that I have for you from Vegas?}
{155}{}{我从维加斯给你的包裹怎么样？ -- What about this package that I have for you from Vegas?}
#{156}{}{What about my help with the Chase case? Isn't that worth anything?}
{156}{}{我帮蔡斯办案怎么样？这不值钱吗？ -- What about my help with the Chase case? Isn't that worth anything?}
#{157}{}{Well, that's enough. I can trust you with one simple task to see how you handle it.}
{157}{}{好了，够了。我可以相信你一个简单的任务，看看你如何处理它。 -- Well, that's enough. I can trust you with one simple task to see how you handle it.}
#{158}{}{Excellent. How can I help, Mr. Bertolini?}
{158}{}{杰出的。我能帮忙吗，伯托里尼先生？ -- Excellent. How can I help, Mr. Bertolini?}
#{159}{}{As long as I get paid, I'm in.}
{159}{}{只要我拿到工资，我就加入了。 -- As long as I get paid, I'm in.}
#{160}{}{In this case, go to the Luciano's ranch on the southern outskirts of the town. There you will find a local beggar, who is known as "The Canary". Tell him "The gilding is gone from our century" and return to me with his answer.}
{160}{}{在这种情况下，去镇南郊的卢西亚诺牧场。在那里你会发现一个当地的乞丐，他被称为“金丝雀”。告诉他“镀金已经从我们的世纪消失了”，然后带着他的答案回到我身边。 -- In this case, go to the Luciano's ranch on the southern outskirts of the town. There you will find a local beggar, who is known as "The Canary". Tell him "The gilding is gone from our century" and return to me with his answer.}
