#{162}{}{Okay.}
{162}{}{可以。 -- Okay.}
#{163}{}{Payment will be received upon the job's completion. But act quietly, so no one from Oliver's commune would suspect anything.}
{163}{}{付款将在工作完成后收到。但要安静行事，这样奥利弗公社的人就不会怀疑任何事情了。 -- Payment will be received upon the job's completion. But act quietly, so no one from Oliver's commune would suspect anything.}
#{164}{}{Understood.}
{164}{}{理解。 -- Understood.}
#{165}{}{I have a package for you from Vegas.}
{165}{}{我有一个从维加斯给你的包裹。 -- I have a package for you from Vegas.}
#{166}{}{I've been waiting for it. What's the matter?}
{166}{}{我一直在等。怎么了 -- I've been waiting for it. What's the matter?}
#{167}{}{I'm having difficulties... }
{167}{}{我有困难。。。 -- I'm having difficulties... }
#{168}{}{Difficulties?! I have paid good money for this product, and now you come to me and say you're "having difficulties"?! I should have resorted to more effective delivery service... I hope, for your own sake, that this was the last screw up, courier.}
{168}{}{困难？！我花了很多钱买这个产品，现在你来找我说你“有困难”？！我应该求助于更有效的送货服务。。。我希望，为了你自己，这是最后一次搞砸了，信使。 -- Difficulties?! I have paid good money for this product, and now you come to me and say you're "having difficulties"?! I should have resorted to more effective delivery service... I hope, for your own sake, that this was the last screw up, courier.}
#{169}{}{Of course, uh, Mr. Bertolini. No more misfires.}
{169}{}{当然，呃，伯托里尼先生。不再缺火。 -- Of course, uh, Mr. Bertolini. No more misfires.}
#{170}{}{I've been waiting for it, but... How did it come into *your* possession!?}
{170}{}{我一直在等，但是。。。你怎么知道的！？ -- I've been waiting for it, but... How did it come into *your* possession!?}
#{171}{}{It's a long story, boss. The short is, I have good connections, and your associates aren't so good at keeping secrets. So - are you interested in package? Or should I throw it out?}
{171}{}{说来话长，老大。简而言之，我人脉很好，你的同事不太善于保守秘密。你对包装感兴趣吗？或者我应该把它扔掉？ -- It's a long story, boss. The short is, I have good connections, and your associates aren't so good at keeping secrets. So - are you interested in package? Or should I throw it out?}
#{172}{}{Hold your tongue, and pray to the gods that I won't shoot you where you stand. This product is too valuable. Many in Reno would sell their souls for the sake of it. I'm clever enough to pay in cash instead. Here's your fee for delivery. Now leave the briefcase and get out.}
{172}{}{闭上你的嘴，向上帝祈祷，我不会在你站的地方射杀你。这个产品太值钱了。雷诺的许多人会为了这个出卖自己的灵魂。我很聪明，可以用现金来代替。这是你的送货费。现在把公文包留下，出去。 -- Hold your tongue, and pray to the gods that I won't shoot you where you stand. This product is too valuable. Many in Reno would sell their souls for the sake of it. I'm clever enough to pay in cash instead. Here's your fee for delivery. Now leave the briefcase and get out.}
#{173}{}{Alright.}
{173}{}{好吧。 -- Alright.}
