#{286}{}{I heard rumors that the one whom my son had to kill, still walks free. I guessed that Huey lacked the guts to do it, which is why I put you to watch over the situation. Instead, you just just shat in front of my house. I'm not going to tolerate this! Security - eliminate him!}
{286}{}{我听说我儿子要杀的那个人仍然逍遥法外。我猜休伊没有勇气这么做，这就是为什么我让你来监视局势。相反，你只是在我家门口。我不能容忍这一切！保安-消灭他！ -- I heard rumors that the one whom my son had to kill, still walks free. I guessed that Huey lacked the guts to do it, which is why I put you to watch over the situation. Instead, you just just shat in front of my house. I'm not going to tolerate this! Security - eliminate him!}
