#{300}{}{I represent the "Cotton" Club. We'd like to negotiate a deal about protection during a concert.}
{300}{}{我代表“棉花”俱乐部。我们想就音乐会期间的保护问题进行谈判。 -- I represent the "Cotton" Club. We'd like to negotiate a deal about protection during a concert.}
#{301}{}{Good idea; I've been offering such a deal for a long time. After all, we are neighbors. Tell the owner of the club that I am willing to contribute to the concert, but with the condition of sharing revenue for each day of it. 35% of the revenue should be delivered to my desk in cash.}
{301}{}{好主意，我提出这样的交易已经很久了。毕竟，我们是邻居。告诉俱乐部老板，我愿意为音乐会捐款，但条件是每天分享收入。收入的35%应该用现金送到我的办公桌上。 -- Good idea; I've been offering such a deal for a long time. After all, we are neighbors. Tell the owner of the club that I am willing to contribute to the concert, but with the condition of sharing revenue for each day of it. 35% of the revenue should be delivered to my desk in cash.}
#{302}{}{We agree to these terms.}
{302}{}{我们同意这些条款。 -- We agree to these terms.}
#{303}{}{We need to think about this proposal.}
{303}{}{我们需要考虑一下这个提议。 -- We need to think about this proposal.}
#{304}{}{Right decision. I will send my men to clarify the contract.}
{304}{}{正确的决定。我将派我的人去澄清合同。 -- Right decision. I will send my men to clarify the contract.}
#{305}{}{Thanks, that's all.}
{305}{}{谢谢，就这些。 -- Thanks, that's all.}
#{1123}{}{Boss, I know a lady who's forced to pay her debts to the casino after the death of her husband. Could you help to resolve this issue?}
{1123}{}{头儿，我认识一位女士，她丈夫死后，她被迫向赌场还债。你能帮忙解决这个问题吗？ -- Boss, I know a lady who's forced to pay her debts to the casino after the death of her husband. Could you help to resolve this issue?}
