{1151}{}{通讯？和谁一起？ -- Communications? With whom... ?}
#{1154}{}{Listen, I wasn't born yesterday. I've handled a lot of jobs in my time... }
{1154}{}{听着，我不是昨天出生的。我这段时间做了很多工作。。。 -- Listen, I wasn't born yesterday. I've handled a lot of jobs in my time... }
